Package renting

Class OngoingTrip

java.lang.Object
renting.OngoingTrip
public class OngoingTrip extends Object
This class describes an ongoing trip. Hence it has no attribute duration but only a start_time since we can deduce its duration at the end with the current time and its starting time.
